    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Rare find alert \u2014 this gem is in absolutely mint condition and ready to turn heads! Every detail has been meticulously maintained, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior that looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. The engine runs with silky-smooth precision, and everything \u2014 we mean everything \u2014 works exactly as it should. If you've been searching for a vehicle you can be truly proud of without any surprises, this is the one you've been waiting for. Don't miss your chance to own a truly exceptional car!",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly in poor condition \u2014 buyers should be fully aware of significant wear and issues before considering a purchase. The exterior shows heavy scratches, dents, and areas of faded or peeling paint across multiple panels. The interior has sustained considerable wear, including torn or heavily stained upholstery, damaged trim pieces, and a worn headliner. Mechanically, the vehicle has known issues that will require attention, and buyers should budget for repairs. This listing is best suited for those seeking a project vehicle, parts car, or an extremely budget-conscious buyer willing to invest in restoration. No warranties are implied or offered.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Looking for a solid, dependable ride that won't break the bank? This vehicle is in genuinely good condition \u2014 it's been well cared for and it shows! The exterior presents nicely with only minor signs of everyday use, and the interior is clean and comfortable. Mechanically, this car runs well and is ready to take you where you need to go. It's not quite showroom-perfect, but it's a trustworthy, quality vehicle that offers real value. Come take it for a spin \u2014 we think you'll be impressed!",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in outstanding mint condition \u2014 a genuinely rare opportunity in the used-car market. The exterior is virtually flawless, featuring a deep, rich paint finish with no visible scratches, dents, or blemishes of any kind. The interior is equally impressive, with pristine upholstery, fully functional controls, and a cabin that looks and smells as fresh as the day it left the showroom. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, with all mechanical systems performing at their best \u2014 no warning lights, no unusual noises, and no deferred maintenance. This is the kind of car that turns heads and inspires confidence, and it has been meticulously cared for throughout its life. A full inspection is welcome and encouraged \u2014 we are confident it will confirm everything described here.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "terse_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "terse_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition with only minor wear, drives well, and has no significant issues.",
